exercises.name: Barbell Back Squat
exercises.instructions: Stand with feet shoulder-width apart, barbell on upper back. Lower into squat position, keeping chest up and knees tracking over toes.

exercises.name: Barbell Front Squat
exercises.instructions: Hold bar across front of shoulders in front rack position. Squat down while keeping torso upright.

exercises.name: Barbell Overhead Squat
exercises.instructions: Hold bar overhead with wide grip. Squat down while maintaining overhead position.

exercises.name: Barbell Bench Press
exercises.instructions: Lie on bench with eyes under barbell. Grip bar slightly wider than shoulders. Lower bar to chest, then press up explosively.

exercises.name: Barbell Incline Bench Press
exercises.instructions: Lie on incline bench set to 30-45 degrees. Press bar from chest level straight up.

exercises.name: Barbell Decline Bench Press
exercises.instructions: Lie on decline bench. Press bar from chest level straight up.

exercises.name: Barbell Close Grip Bench Press
exercises.instructions: Lie on bench with narrow grip on bar. Lower to chest keeping elbows close to body.

exercises.name: Barbell Deadlift
exercises.instructions: Stand with feet hip-width apart, bar over mid-foot. Hinge at hips, grip bar with hands just outside legs.

exercises.name: Barbell Romanian Deadlift
exercises.instructions: Start standing with bar at hip height. Hinge at hips pushing them back while keeping bar close to body.

exercises.name: Barbell Sumo Deadlift
exercises.instructions: Stand with wide stance, toes pointed out. Grip bar inside legs and lift by driving through heels.

exercises.name: Barbell Stiff Leg Deadlift
exercises.instructions: Keep legs relatively straight, hinge at hips to lower bar toward floor.

exercises.name: Barbell Overhead Press
exercises.instructions: Stand with feet hip-width apart, bar at shoulder height. Press bar straight up overhead, keeping core tight.

exercises.name: Barbell Push Press
exercises.instructions: Use leg drive to help press bar overhead. Quick dip and drive through legs.

exercises.name: Barbell Seated Press
exercises.instructions: Sit on bench with back support. Press bar from shoulder level straight up.

exercises.name: Barbell Row
exercises.instructions: Hinge at hips with knees slightly bent, holding barbell with overhand grip. Pull bar to lower chest.

exercises.name: Barbell Pendlay Row
exercises.instructions: Start from dead stop on floor each rep. Pull bar explosively to chest.

exercises.name: Barbell Underhand Row
exercises.instructions: Use underhand grip to emphasize biceps and lower lats.

exercises.name: Barbell T-Bar Row
exercises.instructions: Use T-bar handle or landmine setup. Pull bar to chest with both hands.

exercises.name: Barbell Bicep Curl
exercises.instructions: Stand holding barbell with underhand grip. Curl bar up by flexing biceps, keep elbows stationary.

exercises.name: Barbell Preacher Curl
exercises.instructions: Use preacher bench to isolate biceps. Curl bar up with controlled motion.

exercises.name: Barbell Reverse Curl
exercises.instructions: Use overhand grip to target forearms and brachialis.

exercises.name: Barbell Hip Thrust
exercises.instructions: Sit with upper back against bench, barbell across hips. Drive hips up by squeezing glutes.

exercises.name: Barbell Glute Bridge
exercises.instructions: Lie on floor with bar across hips. Bridge up by squeezing glutes.

exercises.name: Barbell Skull Crusher
exercises.instructions: Lie on bench holding bar above chest. Lower bar to forehead by bending only at elbows.

exercises.name: Barbell Overhead Tricep Extension
exercises.instructions: Stand holding bar overhead. Lower behind head by bending elbows.

exercises.name: Barbell Upright Row
exercises.instructions: Hold bar with narrow overhand grip. Pull bar straight up along body to chest level.

exercises.name: Barbell Shrug
exercises.instructions: Hold bar with overhand grip at hip level. Lift shoulders straight up toward ears.

exercises.name: Barbell High Pull
exercises.instructions: Explosive pull from floor to chest level using hips and shoulders.

exercises.name: Barbell Power Clean
exercises.instructions: Explosive lift from floor to front rack position.

exercises.name: Barbell Clean and Press
exercises.instructions: Clean bar to shoulders then press overhead.

exercises.name: Barbell Thrusters
exercises.instructions: Front squat followed immediately by overhead press.

exercises.name: Barbell Good Morning
exercises.instructions: Bar on shoulders, hinge at hips to bow forward keeping back straight.

exercises.name: Barbell Lunge
exercises.instructions: Bar on shoulders, step forward into lunge position alternating legs.

exercises.name: Barbell Reverse Lunge
exercises.instructions: Bar on shoulders, step backward into lunge position.

exercises.name: Barbell Split Squat
exercises.instructions: Static split stance, lower back knee toward ground.

exercises.name: Barbell Step Up
exercises.instructions: Bar on shoulders, step up onto box or bench.

exercises.name: Barbell Calf Raise
exercises.instructions: Bar on shoulders, rise up on toes.

exercises.name: Barbell Wrist Curl
exercises.instructions: Forearms on bench, curl wrists up and down.

exercises.name: Barbell Reverse Wrist Curl
exercises.instructions: Overhand grip, curl wrists up targeting top of forearms.

exercises.name: Dumbbell Chest Press
exercises.instructions: Lie on bench holding dumbbells at chest level. Press weights up and together.

exercises.name: Dumbbell Incline Press
exercises.instructions: Lie on incline bench with dumbbells at shoulder level. Press up and together.

exercises.name: Dumbbell Decline Press
exercises.instructions: Lie on decline bench with dumbbells at chest level. Press up and together.

exercises.name: Dumbbell Fly

exercises.name: Dumbbell Incline Fly

exercises.name: Dumbbell Decline Fly
exercises.instructions: Lie on decline bench with dumbbells above chest. Lower in arc, bring together.

exercises.name: Dumbbell Pullover
exercises.instructions: Lie on bench holding one dumbbell. Lower over head in arc motion.

exercises.name: Dumbbell Row
exercises.instructions: Place one knee and hand on bench. Pull dumbbell to side of torso with free hand.

exercises.name: Dumbbell Bent Over Row
exercises.instructions: Hinge at hips holding dumbbells. Pull weights to sides of torso, squeezing shoulder blades.

exercises.name: Dumbbell Chest Supported Row

exercises.name: Dumbbell Reverse Fly
exercises.instructions: Bend forward holding dumbbells. Raise weights out to sides, squeezing shoulder blades.

exercises.name: Dumbbell Shoulder Press
exercises.instructions: Sit or stand holding dumbbells at shoulder height. Press weights straight up overhead.

exercises.name: Dumbbell Arnold Press

exercises.name: Dumbbell Front Raise

exercises.name: Dumbbell Rear Delt Fly

exercises.name: Dumbbell Upright Row
exercises.instructions: Hold dumbbells in front of body. Pull up along torso to chest level.

exercises.name: Dumbbell Shrug
exercises.instructions: Hold dumbbells at sides. Lift shoulders straight up toward ears, hold briefly.

exercises.name: Dumbbell Bicep Curl
exercises.instructions: Stand holding dumbbells at sides. Curl weights up by flexing biceps, keep elbows stationary.

exercises.name: Dumbbell Hammer Curl
exercises.instructions: Hold dumbbells with neutral grip. Curl up keeping palms facing each other throughout.

exercises.name: Dumbbell Concentration Curl

exercises.name: Dumbbell Preacher Curl
exercises.instructions: Use preacher bench for support. Curl dumbbell with controlled motion.

exercises.name: Dumbbell Incline Curl
exercises.instructions: Lie on incline bench. Curl dumbbells with arms hanging down.

exercises.name: Dumbbell Tricep Extension
exercises.instructions: Hold dumbbell overhead with both hands. Lower behind head by bending only at elbows.

exercises.name: Dumbbell Tricep Kickback

exercises.name: Dumbbell Skull Crusher

exercises.name: Dumbbell Close Grip Press

exercises.name: Dumbbell Sumo Squat

exercises.name: Dumbbell Lunge

exercises.name: Dumbbell Stiff Leg Deadlift

exercises.name: Dumbbell Step Up
exercises.instructions: Hold dumbbells at sides. Step up onto box or bench, then step back down.

exercises.name: Dumbbell Hip Thrust
exercises.instructions: Upper back on bench, dumbbell on hips. Drive hips up squeezing glutes.

exercises.name: Dumbbell Glute Bridge
exercises.instructions: Lie on floor with dumbbell on hips. Bridge up squeezing glutes.

exercises.name: Dumbbell Calf Raise
exercises.instructions: Hold dumbbell in one hand. Rise up on toes of same side, hold briefly.

exercises.name: Dumbbell Thrusters
exercises.instructions: Hold dumbbells at shoulders. Squat down then press overhead as you stand.

exercises.name: Dumbbell Man Makers

exercises.name: Dumbbell Turkish Get Up

exercises.name: Dumbbell Swing

exercises.name: Dumbbell Snatch

exercises.name: Dumbbell Clean

exercises.name: Dumbbell Renegade Row
exercises.instructions: Plank position on dumbbells, row one weight while stabilizing.

exercises.name: Cable Wide Grip Row

exercises.name: Cable Close Grip Row

exercises.name: Cable Single Arm Row

exercises.name: Cable High Row
